{"tid":1439980,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[心理] 唔好再講個「輸」字！！！","createTime":"2019-08-10T09:43:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T15:59:23.000Z","uid":31710,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"18f8f468511361007076d86d68dd25a8ecef5a70","tid":1439980,"uid":31710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T09:43:48.000Z","msg":"成日見到有人開post話<br />\n「我地會輸」「我地已經輸左」「我地輸緊」<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我明白警世係好緊要！！！</span></span><br />\n但係可以從另一個角度講<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「我地未贏」「我地一定要贏」</span>[/size=5]<br />\n我地要贏呀！！！<br />\n<br />\n開口埋口都話自己輸<br />\n對打仗既士氣根本唔好！<br />\n你自己都會聽到覺得自己唔會贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n即使得0.1%成功都要去搏<br />\n大家唔係因為咁堅持到依家咩？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">依家5大訴求一樣都未達標<br />\n中港又不停玩分化、派3毛轉風向<br />\n警隊又多左個劉業成出黎對付我地<br />\n香港人依2個月個個星期出去搏命<br />\n6個同路人冇左條命 幾百人個比人拉左<br />\n我地唔好白費之前既努力<br />\n救人呀！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n大家記住幾句野！<br />\n[size=6]<span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n不分化 不割蓆 不篤灰 <br />\n核彈 錫春袋都唔割<br />\n香港人冇得輸，一輸就輸永遠</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我地要贏呀！"},{"pid":"6e8c9de37fff6a6cd9f0c23a193752bcab4c15d4","tid":1439980,"uid":142854,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T09:45:21.000Z","msg":"邊個買書拎書就係鬼！！！！"},{"pid":"d6f0015676ecee44de128e9b0577937dedc77f9c","tid":1439980,"uid":3696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T09:45:48.000Z","msg":"緊急！關於港島東反送中反黑大遊行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1439067\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1439067</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0a3f5c4ce4620391bbfa9ca8d00d7bbb4146e84c","tid":1439980,"uid":189068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T09:46:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c8653c369f41af8a03cb00bcd9ce3db528b881af","tid":1439980,"uid":297569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T09:48:17.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d153ef216d8c1e9d96374f332dceb1ef40d9da29","tid":1439980,"uid":31710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T09:51:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dbb2a51b068f2adf371ab484ac0ccf73db28f174","tid":1439980,"uid":31710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T09:52:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0a88a2cf45e73cd73a24788bce2c47ca2bc9b746","tid":1439980,"uid":31710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T09:53:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3af1a0e60faf97c9a6453639e92cf3ccf65cce6e","tid":1439980,"uid":261705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T09:56:44.000Z","msg":"我哋贏咗經驗，但唔夠，要贏多D"},{"pid":"8ba96252838327c4795525c86c07de05a488bc8d","tid":1439980,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T09:57:46.000Z","msg":"push，未贏咋！"},{"pid":"d51216ba21b6cf8dbeb82db1763c30b39789ded4","tid":1439980,"uid":36089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T09:58:02.000Z","msg":"不好意思，借一借位：<br />\n<br />\n求求大家，盡快去換美元現鈔！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1429581\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1429581</a>"},{"pid":"123b85e9a5ff7c186bf7dda6ffb56ab0ba615437","tid":1439980,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T10:00:43.000Z","msg":"提防散水 提防分化"},{"pid":"bac1c572fe5ed4110b375311ba3de40209729bd3","tid":1439980,"uid":31710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T10:03:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c7d7c0f87ec